&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for an experienced nurse to join our team as a Specialist Respiratory Nurse in the Shropshire Community Respiratory Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for applicants with a respiratory background who have excellent respiratory clinical knowledge and skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will involve managing a caseload of patients in the community, triaging new referrals, providing nurse-lead respiratory clinics, nurse-led oxygen clinics and participating in MDT. You will work closely with other Health Professionals especially G.P’s, Community Matrons and hospital specialists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel ready for a challenge and meet the requirements of the post please send us your application form.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The post is for up to 37.5 hours per week, fixed term contract or secondment until 31st March 2021, bank hours will also be considered.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
